reviewText: I am really enjoying queer as folk it is truly entertaining  it make you laugh it makes you cry . I have fallen love with all of the characters  I have all five seasons

I loaned out my full set to some so called friends back when this was first available one disc was missing of course no one knew where it was.
It took a few years but this is what i needed to finish my first season of queer as folk.
Thank you
